  "3028560": {
    "name": "Footsy",
    "steam_appid": 3028560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Footsy是一款以奶奶家为背景的疯狂多人足球派对游戏 ！在这儿，你能尽情砸碎家具、打破瓶子、掀翻电视，投身疯狂的进球大战，绝对是派对的绝佳选择！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/65463ee3ffa2c3631ed73cc7777f0f50.webp?t=1772035997\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来一场1v1的足球对决，踢球、搞破坏，战胜朋友，在奶奶家开启疯狂足球派对！不管是窝在沙发上同屏激战，还是远程联机，这场游戏都将狠狠考验你们的友谊！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/445a6a4ed054d81460a40d7de442c916.poster.avif?t=1772035997\" width=613 height=249 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/445a6a4ed054d81460a40d7de442c916.webm?t=1772035997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/6d16a2f5ee4cf0d9eea5e05028ae880b.webp?t=1772035997\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情发挥，砸桌子、摔花瓶、推倒电视，每场比赛都混乱感拉满。基于物理效果的混战机制，让每一脚都充满变数，不仅能改变比赛局势，还能把房间搅得天翻地覆！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/24181bc88d3e5c37f140c69d53226985.poster.avif?t=1772035997\" width=613 height=235 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/24181bc88d3e5c37f140c69d53226985.webm?t=1772035997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/4870aba82d8ac0fe4ad2cc1ba647dc02.webp?t=1772035997\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只需一个摇杆和一个按钮，就能轻松开启进球之旅。游戏极易上手，就算新手也能迅速融入。但要是想精通，玩家就得钻研时机、瞄准技巧，掌握高级射门方法，称霸赛场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/6b4e8671f8a831354679976b1f23082f.poster.avif?t=1772035997\" width=613 height=235 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/6b4e8671f8a831354679976b1f23082f.webm?t=1772035997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/b35f0ae5a19ef7e351e73017c0f504b6.webp?t=1772035997\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比赛规则完全可以自定义，你可以选择用不用家具，还能挑选足球、冰球，甚至神秘的变形拼图方块来比赛，每场对战都独一无二，充满新鲜感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/7383c40f89e33560af295a33113b20f1.poster.avif?t=1772035997\" width=613 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/7383c40f89e33560af295a33113b20f1.webm?t=1772035997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/486750710b3e882c8e445eed0abdb0fb.webp?t=1772035997\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏里有奶奶家的6个独特房间任你闯荡，每个房间都有专属挑战。能通过马桶瞬间传送，拉狗狗上场搅局，拿奶奶的旧炸弹玩“烫手山芋”，或是用冰块冻住对手，阻碍他们行动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/19d92ede6e5e2e9e5d146d80452bbcd0.poster.avif?t=1772035997\" width=613 height=235 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/19d92ede6e5e2e9e5d146d80452bbcd0.webm?t=1772035997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/9600c9ee64db7f3178bef8d148eba9c0.webp?t=1772035997\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演调皮小孩，角色外观能自由定制。披上狮子装、扮成公主，或是走哥特风，随心所欲展现个性，在打败对手的同时，秀出独特自我！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/098b4c4d9ff88c32a676d0f132446405.poster.avif?t=1772035997\" width=613 height=343 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/098b4c4d9ff88c32a676d0f132446405.webm?t=1772035997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/ed5d4650e9f8142eb75318fc512ca199.webp?t=1772035997\" width=500 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Footsy用手柄玩更带感，Xbox、PlayStation、Switch等手柄统统支持。快喊上朋友，拿起手柄，准备沉浸在疯狂的进球乐趣中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/33941b8b216217ba9df399b1408c7ba2.poster.avif?t=1772035997\" width=616 height=279 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/33941b8b216217ba9df399b1408c7ba2.webm?t=1772035997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还能通过Steam的Remote Play Together功能一起联机。不过要注意，视频画质和输入延迟会受网络速度与硬件性能影响 。</p>",
